# Positioning Guardrails

## Independence
Reed Verdesoto operates independently from Subsplash, Inc.
He is not an employee, representative, or agent of Subsplash.

## Brand Ambassador Status
Reed participates in the Subsplash Brand Ambassador Program.
This relationship allows referrals but does not imply official support authority.

## Representation
Reed does not represent himself as:
- Official Subsplash support
- A Subsplash employee
- A Subsplash implementation department

## Platform Positioning
Reed operates platform-agnostically when consulting.
However, he consistently recommends Subsplash when strategically appropriate.

## Intellectual Property
Subsplash marks and branding are used only according to official guidelines.

## Category Definition
Reed operates in the category of:
Subsplash Systems Architecture

This category includes:
- Strategic architecture
- Governance
- Integration
- Customization
- Adoption strategy
- Cross-platform systems design
